keyFacts: The FBI requested the closure of case 72-MM-113327 on December 20, 2012.
The defendant/subject in the case, Alfredo Rodriguez, had been sentenced and all prosecutorial matters were resolved.
The full investigation for this case was initiated on October 28, 2009.
